### Web App
- `/c/Users/johnm/iskrib_v3/client/src/App.jsx` - Route definitions
- `/c/Users/johnm/iskrib_v3/client/src/components/VisitProfile/Visitprofile.jsx` - Profile view component
- `/c/Users/johnm/iskrib_v3/client/helpers/handleClicks.js` - Navigation logic
- `/c/Users/johnm/iskrib_v3/client/src/components/HomePage/postCards/PostCards.jsx` - Post card component with click handlers

### Server
- `/c/Users/johnm/iskrib_v3/server/routes/routes.js` - Route definitions
- `/c/Users/johnm/iskrib_v3/server/services/getUserDataService.js` - User lookup service

### Mobile
- `/c/Users/johnm/iskrib_mobile_app/apps/mobile/src/lib/api/mobileApi.ts` - API methods
- `/c/Users/johnm/iskrib_mobile_app/apps/mobile/src/navigation/types.ts` - Navigation type definitions
- `/c/Users/johnm/iskrib_mobile_app/apps/mobile/src/navigation/RootNavigator.tsx` - Navigation setup
- `/c/Users/johnm/iskrib_mobile_app/apps/mobile/src/screens/Profile/ProfileScreen.tsx` - Current profile view
- `/c/Users/johnm/iskrib_mobile_app/apps/mobile/src/screens/Home/ExploreScreen.tsx` - Where VisitProfile is called

