### Step 7 (optional but recommended): Navigate to own Profile tab from VisitProfile if userId matches self

**File:** `C:\Users\johnm\iskrib_mobile_app\apps\mobile\src\screens\Profile\VisitProfileScreen.tsx`

Add a guard at the top of the component that redirects to the Profile tab if the visited user is the logged-in user:

```typescript
const {user} = useAuth();

React.useEffect(() => {
  if (user?.id && userId === user.id) {
